{"tid":1061742,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"裸上身自拍相做證 許廷鏗希雲街通宵會女友？","createTime":"2019-03-14T15:04:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-15T02:37:37.000Z","uid":227995,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"ccbdac8c623fb50f464cb36cbe6a9bd63c2d94b4","tid":1061742,"uid":227995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T15:04:05.000Z","msg":"許廷鏗演唱會前既白滑肉照爆光?<br />\n<br />\n許廷鏗（Alfred）09年參加歌唱比賽入行，之後一邊做牙醫，一邊發展歌唱事業，今年是他入行第10年，早前更宣佈3月會在紅館舉行演唱會。<br />\n由於Alfred屬唱得之人，故多年來獲不少前輩讚賞，亦有不少歌迷愛戴，但他甚少與異性傳緋聞，相反經常出現「斷背」疑雲，和胡鴻鈞亦曾經傳緋聞，惟兩人對緋聞均一笑置之，胡鴻鈞更講笑說他們出雙入對多年。<br />\n<br />\nAlfred早前在演唱會記招被女模狂咀後，亦自爆dry了很久沒有拍拖，不過近日有讀者楊先生向《蘋果》爆料，指Alfred頻頻約人在銅鑼灣希雲街密會。前年Alfred在歌曲《神奇之旅》填上幾句歌詞「我信一天會遇上極光，為求環抱星與夢竭力前望，路過希雲街當它冰島札幌」，之後說過詞中這3個地方 對他有微妙意思，想不到今次被指密會的地方，剛巧又在希雲街，而據知他在那裏有一個和胞兄持有的物業單位。<br />\n<br />\n讀者楊先生報料指，其好友向他表示，身邊有朋友正跟Alfred秘密來往，除了在農曆新年到訪Alfred位於大圍寓所，由凌晨3時至早上9時多一直單獨相處，之後再有相約去銅鑼灣希雲街見面，同樣過了一整晚才離開。<br />\n<br />\n楊先生坦言，一班朋友本來都有懷疑，但3月2日，楊先生朋友的友人又約了Alfred，大家於是齊齊在希雲街守候，結果在晚上接近10時，果真見到Alfred出現，他急急腳走上了一座唐樓，友人更把朋友分享給他的「福利圖」發送給大家看，包括兩張Alfred對着鏡的自拍照，其中一張Alfred更是赤裸上身，露出白滑肚皮。不過，楊先生報料時表示友人未有透露相約Alfred的朋友是男是女，表示要保障朋友，只估計Alfred相約的是女性。<br />\n<br />\n今日《蘋果》透過唱片公司聯絡Alfred，欲問他是否曾到希雲街？是否約了女友人？以及對私人自拍照流出可感不開心？但Alfred透過唱片公司表示：「不回應了！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mfuW5vi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmfuW5vi.jpg&h=ef2438d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UDjHgBY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUDjHgBY.jpg&h=acfa4ab3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190313/59361955\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190313%2F59361955&d=%2FIrJ3RR%2Fwz8SFLZOEAJhprnp9gp%2BSvHPFRLSSJzTNPo%3D&h=5f342f77\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190313%2F59361955&h=dc641ba5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190313/59361955</a>"},{"pid":"30292fbc915e9c778a1862689fd10ff1b2c25055","tid":1061742,"uid":21423,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T15:05:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7db441f1dd044261e346e5382ae26d6827fcd085","tid":1061742,"uid":36253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T15:28:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b70f587942192e471ac8551d31721fecf86e649","tid":1061742,"uid":224533,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T15:46:18.000Z","msg":"女友人係咪欣宜"},{"pid":"883b5c91475e9026de4ea99b91e61d5bb697ebdc","tid":1061742,"uid":185126,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T15:56:21.000Z","msg":"肌都無啲邊個會想食佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd71b98e11b8dac4bdd8468f733091be06720221","tid":1061742,"uid":58140,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T15:57:02.000Z","msg":"一睇就知係0仔"},{"pid":"3d40fe9ed95f34cb140872fa3ecce4b16935c4d6","tid":1061742,"uid":132587,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T15:57:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/08/202508_d2f86ed4035c7082f01a504345f60226.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F08%2F202508_d2f86ed4035c7082f01a504345f60226.png&h=64c3f061&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a0b1437c61f56fdb1b5521a04b67d509402ffcf0","tid":1061742,"uid":56716,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T16:09:29.000Z","msg":"咩朋友咁賤會出賣佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01339601c9b36cf628dc270ca421d82a87513505","tid":1061742,"uid":227995,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"cited